===新系統分類===
現時這些昆蟲被簡單分為兩個分類單元：[[南翅亞目|南翅亞目]]（[[Antarctoperlaria|Antarctoperlaria]]，即再早期分類的[[古襀翅亞目|古襀翅亞目]]，[[Archiperlaria|Archiperlaria]]）及{{tsl|en|北翅亞目}}（{{tsl|en|Arctoperlaria}}）兩大類<ref>{{cite web |url=http://plecoptera.speciesfile.org/Common/basic/Taxa.aspx?TaxonNameID=1152749 |title=order Plecoptera |work=order Plecoptera: Plecoptera Species File |edition=5.0 |access-date=2020-06-02 |language=en |archive-date=2020-07-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200706170040/http://plecoptera.speciesfile.org/Common/basic/Taxa.aspx?TaxonNameID=1152749 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。然而，前者只簡單包括兩個屬於[[基群|基群]]的總科，而這兩個總科似乎並沒有任何緊密關係，因此被認為不是一個自然的分類單元<ref>{{cite web |author=C. Riley Nelson |work=[[Tree_of_Life_Web_Project|Tree of Life Web Project]] |url=http://tolweb.org/Plecoptera/8245/1996.01.01 |title=Plecoptera. Stoneflies |date=January 1, 1996 |access-date=2008-07-31 |language=en |archive-date=2019-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191006214758/http://tolweb.org/Plecoptera/8245/1996.01.01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

北翅亞目可再分為兩個[[下目|下目]]，即：
* [[Euholognatha|Euholognatha]]或[[Filipalpia|Filipalpia]]（原來的[[絲翅亞目|絲翅亞目]]）；以及
* [[Systellognatha|Systellognatha]]、[[Setipalpia|Setipalpia]]或[[Subulipalpia|Subulipalpia]]。
除卻[[Scopuridae|Scopuridae]]應被包括在北翅亞目的基群科，但未能安排到任何一個下目之外，其餘分類單元均與[[系統發生樹|系統發生樹]]相對應。
Alternatively, the Scopuridae were placed in an unranked <!-- [[clade|clade]] -->[[演化支|演化支]] "Holognatha" together with the Euholognatha (meaning roughly "advanced Holognatha"), but the Scopuridae do not appear significantly closer to the Euholognatha than to the Systellognatha.{{Citation needed|date=October 2008}}

In addition, not adopting the clades Antarctoperlaria and Holognatha allows for a systematic layout of the Plecoptera that adequately reproduces phylogeny, while retaining the traditional <!-- [[Taxonomic_rank|ranked taxa]] -->[[分类阶元|分类阶元]].<ref name="Zwick"/><ref>Nelson (1996b)</ref>

此外，無論是新分類還是舊分類，均未包括只有化石種的分類，例如：[[近卷科|近卷科]]（[[Mesoleuctridae|Mesoleuctridae]]）<ref name="Fossilworks">{{Cite web |url = http://fossilworks.org/?a=taxonInfo&taxon_no=228456 |title = Fossilworks: Mesoleuctra |language = en |accessdate = 2017-12-31 |archive-date = 2019-02-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190220214021/http://fossilworks.org/?a=taxonInfo&taxon_no=228456 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。

